water conditions or of thecontroversysurrounding the issue.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mislawchukmade\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"no mentionof\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"the water conditions\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead attributing hisvomitingto pushing himself beyond his limits.\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hisvomitingto\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2628}, {\"ngram\": \"his limits\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I pushed myself and throughout the race so many times,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[So] when I started hurting, I just said [to myself] 'twenty more seconds, just stay on for twenty more seconds' and I repeated that too many times to count.\\\"\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"twenty more seconds\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"twenty more seconds\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"too many times\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadian star affirms to feel proud of his performance despite the pain he was in, adding that just getting to participate in the competition was a victory for him.\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 3065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2901, \"end\": 2909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9465657370865104, \"rank\": 0.05482140609131672, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2955}, {\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 2964, \"